Package WordCounter

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CONSTANTS
    Constants interface that is used to provide easy of use for changing the web page URL and directory locations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Connect
    This is a fairly basic class that is used for storing and accessing the parameters that are associated with word objects.
    Controller
    Controller for the graphical user interface.
    Main
    Main class that extends Application as a JavaFX entry point.
    StringCleaner
    Class for normalizing text.
    WebSaver
    Method that is used to read a source page.
    Word
    Word object that is used to store word name and occurrences.
    WordCounter
    This class is used to count post-normalized text from a specified .txt directory.
    WriteToFile
    Class definition used to write a string to a text file.
